<L>__{exterior the castorini house dawn}
<A>__{we watch the effect of the sun coming up on the house. it begins in darkness, and goes through the many graduations of light very quickly until it's lit by the light of bright morning.}
<B>__{the front door opens and the old man and the dogs come out}
<A>__{he's got them on their leashes and, over his head, he carries the black umbrella. he walks off toward the park and disappears.}
